title: The SUPRA Crown Coalition Pistol Featuring Lucien Clarke
description: Up from the underworld comes the limited edition Crown Coalition Pistol from SUPRA. Cloaked in an expanse of khaki suede and twill atop a classic vulcanized sole, the Pistol's colors and insignia are inspired by an age old organization shrouded in shadows. Gold metal eyelets add an air of regal flare while red Crown Coalition emblems adorn the Pistol's heel, tongue, and sock liner. The Crown Coalition Pistol will be available for a limited time exclusively at Crown Coalition dealers starting March 15th. To learn more or to find a Crown Coalition dealer near you visit http://www.suprafootwear.com.
